{
  "stem": "11174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I used to go as a teenager, early teenager, used to go to collect money before Shabbos to help out the few families that were-- that were officially poor.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I still don't know to some of these people-- and this is not one or two, maybe 20 or so-- until this day, how they lived, how they existed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "One, one little-- I don't know if it's interesting to you that one person that I was pretty close with and here and there he came to me, maybe I can lend him a zloty or two.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I did, and here and there he can give it back to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "One day he says I can't give it back to you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I don't know when.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by the way, this is-- he told it to me how it go, but others, some may not even have that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was at least a quarter of the town, of that, that little town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was another one who, as I told you, you used to go here and there to the villages, buy some products, and come into the city and sell it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were also poor, but they may have already for a piece of chicken for Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And instead of eating bread with, with coffee for breakfast, they may even had once in awhile a piece of butter.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But very poor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then there was the so-called middle class who had some sort of businesses in town, or they had some son or daughter in America who helped them a little more.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were the middle class.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
